title: DJ Lou Has A Bumble Fumble & Big Jay Has A Battle Rap (w/ Ron Funches & Ralph Sutton)
description: DJ Lou self sabotage's his bumble game by lashing out at innocent question. Ron Funches joins the show and tells us about running into Crips in the Chicago Library. Ralph Sutton, co-host of "The SDR Show" comes on to discuss his battle rap with Big Jay.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
